http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Archibald\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Archibald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Archibald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Archibald\"}, {\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.207464645364862e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Finucane's rival\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"the superstar\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"her leg\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"a freak accident\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"her garden\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet the team pursuit line-up will most likely either win gold or silver behind New Zealand, a race that is too close to call.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9986144441271839, \"rank\": 0.0011640085910876751, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"line-up\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the men's pursuit line-up should also be in the mix for the top spot on the podium, despite one of the line-up, Dan Bigham, suffering a crash in practice at the velodrome this week.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's pursuit line-up\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"the top spot\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the line-up\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"Dan Bigham\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"a crash\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"the velodrome\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions Incredible days out and trips for autumn and winter Ethan Hayter is a prime candidate for omnium gold and will likely be in contention in the madison with Ollie Wood.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2796, \"end\": 2812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ethan Hayter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"trips\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"autumn\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"a prime candidate\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"omnium gold\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2965}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"the madison\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3013}, {\"ngram\": \"Ollie Wood\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But attention from today onwards looks likely to rest firmly on Finucane, who is not unaware of the expectation, at least within British Cycling circles.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3165, \"end\": 3180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"Finucane\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectation\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to deny that I'd love to win gold,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it's going to be hard.\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as I do everything right, then everything is possible, whether that's gold or not.\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3370, \"entitie